headline: Starbucks Earnings: Why Turnaround CEO Brian Niccol Needs Investors to Stay Patient
summary: Few bosses have enjoyed a warmer welcome than Brian Niccol.  Niccol wants Starbucks to refocus on customers by staffing up, and he wants to alleviate service snafus.  Doing so carries upfront costs, and the question is: Do Niccol's efforts beat the alternative of tinkering around the edges of the huge global chain?
